    {
      "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-8048-9e45-ff1a0d54f496",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Independent selection of learning goals and teammates is especially relevant in online contexts. The authors extract behaviors from the LMS, text that is generated and p+ersonal attributes to perform a social network analysis to identify collaborator relationship networks. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-8048-9e45-ff1a0d54f496",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
